{"tid":1281895,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡大學新校長有野講","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:19:45.000Z","uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"efef288b8cdbce2fc217e5668eab5830da8ffa3e","tid":1281895,"uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"Dear Colleagues and Students <br />\n<br />\nLike many of you, I am deeply saddened by the storming of the Legislative Council Complex on 1 July. While we are fully aware of the sentiments in our society, we are very concerned about the wellness and well-being of our students. <br />\n<br />\nIn any situation, violence can never be a means to resolve problems. Hong Kong&rsquo;s greatest strength &ndash; the rule of law &ndash; is one of its core values and the cornerstone of its success for decades. Sharing a common goal that Hong Kong will continue to be a pluralistic, free, accommodating and peaceful community, we hope people with different views yet on the ground of mutual respect, would build constructive conversations in a calm, rational and peaceful manner to resolve the current divisions. <br />\n<br />\nBest regards <br />\n<br />\nJin-Guang Teng <br />\nPresident <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n各位同事、各位同學： <br />\n<br />\n對於七月一日立法會大樓的衝擊事件，我和你們一樣深感痛心。我們一方面十分明白社會上的情緒，另一方面也非常關注同學的安全和福祉。 <br />\n<br />\n無論在任何情況下，暴力始終不是解決問題的方法。法治是香港的核心價值之一，也是香港數十年來賴以成功的基石。我們希望本著共同的目標，令香港繼續成為一個多元自由、寬容和平的社會，冀盼各方即使持不同意見，仍能在互相尊重的基礎上，以冷靜、理性及和平的方式建立具建設性的對話，以化解當前的矛盾。 <br />\n<br />\n校長 <br />\n滕錦光"},{"pid":"5478059f3979a1de9d70b26ccc04cfeef638588c","tid":1281895,"uid":176081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"Blah blah blah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2279fcef44b64f4290ec1ef473ecd8c7252b03ac","tid":1281895,"uid":35231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦大陸佬"},{"pid":"8deda0e076